The people of Greater Egypt congratulate you on the new Hijri year and the nation at the height of its revolution, and its youth at the height of their determination and their words.
I congratulate you and I am heartened by the continuation of your revolution against this coup d'état and its leaders who want to subjugate the nation and their identities.
The coup d'état and its leaders are afraid of a black fate as punishment for their crimes committed against this great people.
I can not fail to state clearly that I have rejected and still reject all attempts to negotiate the principles of the Revolution and the blood of martyrs

Attempts to negotiate the constants of the revolution and the blood of the martyrs are intended to continue the criminals, and to support the enslavement of a people who never deserved to belong to him.
I emphasize my instructions to the active revolutionaries on the ground that "no recognition of the coup, no retreat from the revolution, nor negotiate the blood of the martyrs" # President

Every year you are free revolutionaries, but I am convinced by the grace of God is not shaken by the victory of Allah for our Revolution and my confidence is not shaking in your steadfast determination and your great sorrow.

God willing, I will not leave my prison before my sons are arrested and I will not enter my dads before my daughters who are well-known detainees, and not my life is more precious than the righteous martyrs.

Azmi derived from the determination of the creative youth in the fields of revolution and its universities and did not and will not forget my children from the recruits who are martyrs who are affected by treachery treachery # President
